it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core.std

Interface InnerName

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InnerName, LinkEntity, LinkFacet, Named, Owned, Point

    public interface InnerName
extends Point, LinkFacet, InnerName
    Inner names are points accessible through the inner interface (whereas ports are not) identified by their name (cf. Named). Inner names (like outer ones) are link facets comparison is based on their name.
    See Also:
    LinkFacet, Point
